data.meta_description:
23 likes, 3 comments - bhamiltonwastaken on April 3, 2024: "“Palo Alto (to Pretoria)” by @slowcollapse 

From the new record “The Freest Speech Ever Attempted Without Disintegrating.” A record about Elon Musk, probably. 

Thank you to AI models of Bad Bunny, Lana Del Rey, Hank Williams Sr., Hank Williams Jr., Serena Williams, William F. Buckley, Will Smith, William Gibson, SpongeBob SquarePants, Elon Musk, Sonic the Hedgehog, Albert Einstein, Nina Hagen, Donald Fagen, John Wayne, Wayne Knight, Mickey Mouse, Donald Rumsfeld, Bart Simpson, James Baldwin, Alec Baldwin, Joe Biden, Joe Rogan, Hulk Hogan, Richard Nixon, Willie Dixon, Angela Merkel, Studs Terkel, Hatsune Miku, Shakira, 21 Savage, and Macho Man Randy Savage for singing. 

The working title for this song was “We Aren’t the World.” Very clever. Goodbye. 

#bhamilton #hashtags".
